{"tid":2244876,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–瀕危物種海南長臂猿","createTime":"2020-10-15T21:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T03:12:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d81ae1ed0a229818d40d1b9f451d3940a124f7","tid":2244876,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T21:37:12.000Z","msg":"海南長臂猿全球數量只剩30隻，聚居在海南森林裡，屬全球頻危動物十大之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xammZ8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxammZ8c.png&h=6a7677a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牠們擁有獨特的習性，近乎不會在陸地行走，只會在繁盛的樹冠中跳躍走動。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）然而，在颱風天災及人為活動的影響下，榭木數量逐漸減少，導致牠們的悽息地面積越來越細，越漸孤立。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCfSnmA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCfSnmA.png&h=7aa19f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）其中有科學家發現（Ref1)，一場颱風過後摧毀了不少樹木，使長臂猿慣常的路徑有所變動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fjyc6Oi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjyc6Oi.png&h=7e43729c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本應無縫連接著樹冠的地方出現相隔約10米的缺口，有不少臂猿均挽有猶豫態度應否飛躍對面，而飛躍過程中亦甚為驚險。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）科學家最後找來爬樹高手，共花上5000美元建造兩條吊橋連接樹冠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5zWO1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5zWO1H.png&h=885326f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吊橋建成176日後，才有第一隻長臂猿嘗試試用，隨後亦招來不少年輕臂猿用上各種方式行走。<br />\n但根據他們的觀察，年長的長臂猿依舊照用跳樹的方式走動，觀察小組只有錄得年長的長臂猿一次的吊橋使用。<br />\n<br />\n吊橋的建立，明顯只是短期的解決辦法。<br />\n如何有效保育頻危物種及預防物種頻危化，是一道所有人也應該深思的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"red\">like</span>以及<span class=\"green\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzurBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=e68afb46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzurBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=a28eba3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-72641-z#Sec13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-020-72641-z%23Sec13&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzurBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=e860728a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-020-72641-z#Sec13</a>"},{"pid":"9d42c988887b1bbc068ae88a7236c036a2db701c","tid":2244876,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T21:37:50.000Z","msg":"5點出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1664b201bda7c681605364f5d6608c7c14b09f5","tid":2244876,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T21:38:55.000Z","msg":"得返三十幾隻基因多樣性唔多夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd925dbac4daf843997a15e68890179636c1c0f","tid":2244876,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d42c988887b1bbc068ae88a7236c036a2db701c","tid":2244876,"uid":16871,"like":0,"d